If you have lost your credit card or if it was stolen, you shall:
                    1. Contact your bank immediately requesting the cancellation of your credit card;
                    2. Send an email to suporte@parcelaja.pt informing that the credit card has been cancelled;
                    3. Parcela Já will send a document you will need to fill out with your new credit card details and we will add it to your instalment plan.
